\id EPH - Dawro 
\h Efesoona 
\toc3 Efe 
\toc2 Efesoona 
\toc1 Efesoona 
\mt2 Phawuloosi 
\mt1 Efesoona Asaw 
\mt2 Xaafeedda Kiitaa 
\imt1 Geluwaa 
\ip Phawuloosi Efesoonan de7iya asaassi xaafeedda kiitaan ubbabaappe aathiide I xeelleeddawe, “Xoossaa qofaa oosuwan peeshshanawe saluwaaninne sa7an de7iyaabay ubbay ittippe shiiqiide, itti Kiristtoosa maataa garssan aqiyaa wodii gakkana” yaagiyaa qofaa (1:10). Hewaa bollankka gujay Yesuusi Kiristtoosanna ittippe gidiide, asaa zariyaa ubbay ittuwaa gidana mala, ha wolqqaama qofaa oosuwan peeshshanaadan Xoossaa asaa hassayissee. 
\ip Efesoona Kiitay koyro saan xaafii ittippetethaawaa xaafanaw doommeeddawaa aassiide, Xoossay Aawuu bare asaa wooti dooreeddentto, unttunttukka A na7aa, Yesuusi Kiristtoosan barenttu nagaraappe maarettiide, waani la77a keseeddenttonne Xoossaa wolqqaama hidootaa qaalay Geeshsha Ayyaanaa bagganna wooti eretteeddentto odee. Laa7ethiyaa shaakuwan qassi xaafii ha kiitaa nabbabiyaawanttu barenttu ittippetethaa de7uwan Kiristtoosan unttunttussi de7iya ittippetethay tuma gidana mala unttunttu waaniide de7anaw bessintto qofissee. 
\ip Asay Kiristtoosan de7iya ittippetethaan waaniide de7anaw danddayintto dumma dumma hiilla haasayan qoncceedda. Ammaniyaa asay itti asatethaa leemisuwaa gidiyaa wode, Kiristtoosi he asatethaw huuphiyaa gidee. Ammaniyaa asay gimbbiyaa golliyaan leemisettiyaa wode, Kiristtoosi he gimbbiyaa gollew godaa xaphuwaa minissiyaa waanna shuchchaa gidee. Ammaniyaa asay machchiyaadan leemisettiyaa wode, Kiristtoosi asinaadan gidee. Xaafiyaawe Kiristtoosa bagganna qoncceedda Xoossaa aadho keekatethaa daro dhoqqissi nashshi haasayiidde, ciimmateedda qofaa shiishshee. I ubbabaakka Kiristtoosa siiquwan, I yarshshettowan, A maarotethan, A aadho keekatethaaninne A sarotethaa bagganna xeellee. 
\iot Shemppatuwaa Ubbatuwaassi Imetteedda Qantha Qofatuwaa 
\io1 Geluwaa (1:1-2) 
\io1 Kiristtoosanne ammaniyaa asaa (1:3-3:21) 
\io1 Kiristtoosan beettiyaa oratha de7uwaa (4:1-6:20) 
\io1 Wursethaa qutiyaa (6:21-24) 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Taani Xoossaa sheniyaan Kiristtoosi Yesuusi kiitteedda Phawuloosi, Efesoonan de7iya Xoossaa naanaw qassi Kiristtoosa Yesuusaw ammanettiide de7iyaawanttoo ha dabidaabbiyaa xaafay. 
\p  
\v 2 Xoossaa nu Aawuwaappenne Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosappe aadho keekatethayinne sarotethay hinttenttoo gido. 
\s1 Kiristtoosappe Beettiyaa Ayyaanaa Anjjuwaa 
\p  
\v 3 Ayyaanaa anjjuwaa ubbaan Kiristtoosa bagganna bolla saluwaan nuuna anjjeedda Xoossaa, nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa Aawuwaa, nuuni galateetto.  
\v 4 Nuuni A sinthan geeshshatuwaanne pokkuu bayinnawantta gidana mala, Xoossay nuuna sa7ay medhettanaappe kase, Kiristtoosa bagganna bare siiquwan dooreedda.  
\v 5 Xoossay bare sheniyaan bare doseeddawaadan, Yesuusi Kiristtoosa bagganna nuuna bare naanatuwaa oothanaw kasetiide qoppi wotheedda.  
\v 6 Xoossay bare siiqiyaa Na7aa bagganna nuussi coo immeedda aadho keekatethaa bonchchuwaa diraw, nuuppe galataa akkanaw hewaa ootheedda. 
\p  
\v 7 Nuuni Xoossaa aadho keekatethaa daruwaadan, Kiristtoosa suuthan wozetteeddo; hewan Xoossay nu nagaraa atto geedda.  
\v 8 Xoossay bare aadhdheedda eratethaa ubbaaninne bare wozanaa qofaa ubbaan bare aadho keekatethaa nuussi darissiide immeedda.  
\v 9 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay bare qoppeeddawaa ootheedda; qassi Kiristtoosa bagganna polanaw qoppi wotheedda xuura yewuwaa nuuna erisseedda.  
\v 10 Xoossay wodiyaa wurssethay gakkiya wode polanaw qoppeedda qofay Kiristtoosa waanna udiide, saluwaaninne sa7an de7iya medhetaa ubbaa ittippe aani shiishshanawaa. 
\p  
\v 11 Ubbabay Xoossaa qofaadaaninne I geeddawaadan haneedda; Xoossay kasetiide qoppi wotheeddawaadan, Kiristtoosa bagganna nuuni aawantta gidanaadan, nuuna dooreedda.  
\v 12 Nuuni kasetiide, Kiristtoosa bagganna akkana giide nashechchan naagiyaawanttu, Xoossaa bonchchuwaa galateetto.  
\v 13 Hinttewukka qassi hewaadan haneedda; tumu kiitaa, hinttenttoo atotethaa aheedda mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa, hintte siseedda wode Kiristtoosa ammaneeddita; Xoossay hinttenttoo immana geedda Geeshsha Ayyaanaa bagganna, hintte Aawaa gidiyaawaa erissiyaa maatafaa hintte bolla wotheedda.  
\v 14 Xoossay bare asaw immana geeddawaa nuuni laattana gakkanaw, Geeshsha Ayyaanaa waasetethaa oyqqeeddo. Hewe qassi A bonchchuwassi, galataa gidanawa. 
\s1 Phawuloosi Efesoona Asaw Woosseedda 
\p  
\v 15 Hewaa diraw, Godaa Yesuusa hintte ammaniyaawaanne geeshshatuwaa ubbaa hintte siiqiyaawaa taani sisoodeppe doommaade,  
\v 16 hinttenttoo Xoossaa galatiyaawaa aggabeyikke; Xoossaa woossaadde hinttewukka woossay.  
\v 17 Qassi Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa Xoossay, bonchchuwaa Aawuu, Xoossaa hintte eranaadan, hinttena aadhdheedda eranchcha oothiyaa qassi Xoossaa hinttenttoo qonccissiyaa Geeshsha Ayyaanaa hinttenttoo immanaadan, taani woossay.  
\v 18 Xoossay hintte akkana giide, nashechchan naagi utteeddawoo hinttena xeeseeddawaanne I bare asaw immana giya anjjuu ay keenaa durentto hintte eranaadan, Xoossay hintte wozanaa dooyyina, A poo7uwaa hintte be7anaadan, taani Xoossaa woossay. 
\p  
\v 19-20 Qassi A ammaniyaa nuunan A wolqqay loythi oothee. Ha nuunan de7iya wolqqaynne hayiquwaappe Kiristtoosa denthiide, saluwaa sa7an Xoossaappe ushechcha bagganna \f + \fr 1:19-20 \fq ushechcha bagga: \ft Wolqqaanne bonchchuwaa sa7aa.\f* utisseedda wolqqaama wolqqay ittuwaa. \x - \xo 1:19-20 \xt Maz 110:1\x* 
\v 21 Kiristtoosi saluwaa sunthatuwaappe, godatethay de7iyaawanttuppe, wolqqaamatuwaappenne godatuwaa ubbaappe bolla gidiide mooddee; I ha77i de7iyaa yeleta xalalaan gidennaan, sinthaappe yaana yeletaanikka hara sunthatethaa ubbaappe dhoqqee.  
\v 22 Xoossay ubbabaa Kiristtoosa gediyaappe garssan moodissiide, qassi Xoossay I ubbabaani ubbaappe bollanna Godaa gidanaadan, woosa gollew A immeedda. \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Maz 8:6\x*\x - \xo 1:22 \xt Qol 1:18\x* 
\v 23 Woosa gollii Kiristtoosa asatethaa; woosa gollii Kiristtoosi ubbasan ubbabaa kunthiyaa A poluwaa. 
\c 2  
\s1 Kiristtoosan Hayiquwaappe De7oo Pinniyaawaa 
\p  
\v 1 Hintte azazettennan ixxeedda dirawunne hintte nagaraa diraw, kase wodiyaan ayyaana hayiquwaa hayiqqeeddita.  
\v 2 He wode hintte ha alamiyaa yeletaa iita ogiyaa hametteeddita; carkkuwaa giddon de7iya wolqqaama ayyaanatuwaa kaappoo qassi Xoossaw azazettenna asaa ha77i mooddiyaa ayyaanaw azazetteeddita.  
\v 3 Nuunikka qassi ubbay he asaa mala; qassi nuuni nu ashuwaa amuwaadan de7eeddo; nu ashuunne nu wozanay koyyeeddawaa ootheeddo. Nuunikka haratuwawaadan, nu medhetaan Xoossaa hanqquwaa akkanaw de7eetto. 
\p  
\v 4 Shin Xoossaa maarotethay dara gidiyaa diraw, bare siiquwaa daruwaadan,  
\v 5 Nuuni aw azazettennan ixxiide, haray atto ayyaanan hayiqqeeddawantta gidinakka, I Kiristtoosanna nuussi de7uwaa immeedda. Xoossaa aadho keekatethan hintte atteeddita.  
\v 6 Nuuni Kiristtoosi Yesuusanna saluwaanne sa7aanne mooddanaadan, Xoossay nuuna aananna ittippe hayiquwaappe dentheedda.  
\v 7 I sinthappe yaana wodiyaan, nuussi Kiristtoosi Yesuusan de7iya keekatethan, ubbaappe aadhdhiyaa bare aadho keekatethaa dhoqqatethaa bessanaw hewaa ootheedda.  
\v 8 Ayissi gooppe, hintte Xoossaa aadho keekatethan, ammanuwan atteeddita; hawe Xoossaa imuwaappe attin, hintte oosuwaanna gidenna.  
\v 9 Hintte daaburan beettibeenna diraw, hintte ceeqettiyaabay ayayiinne baawa.  
\v 10 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni Xoossaa medhetaa; I nuussi kasetiide giigissi wotheedda lo77o oosuwaa nuuni oothanaadan, Kiristtoosi Yesuusa bagganna nuuna medhdheedda. 
\s1 Kiristtoosan Beettiyaa Ittippetethaa 
\p  
\v 11 Hewaa diraw, hinttenoo zariyaan Ayihuda gidenna asatoo, barenttu asatethaa bolla kushiyan oosetteeddawan, barena qaxxaretteeddawantta giya Ayihudatuu, qaxxarettibeennawantta giide xeesiyaawanttoo, hintte kase oonentto akeekite.  
\v 12 He wode hintte Kiristtoosappe shaaketteeddita; imatha gidiide, Israa7eeliyaa asaappe haakkiide de7eeddita; Xoossay bare asaw immana giide caaqqeedda caaquwaappe ayinne demmibeykkita; ha sa7aa bolla hintte demmana giide, nashechchan naagi utteeddawaa demmennaaninne qassi Xoossay bayinnaan de7eeddita.  
\v 13 Shin hintte kase haakkiide de7iyaawanttu ha77i Kiristtoosa Yesuusanna de7iide, Kiristtoosa hayiquwan mataa shiiqeeddita. 
\p  
\v 14 Ayissi gooppe, Kiristtoosi Ayihuda asaanne Ayihuda gidenna asaa ittuwaa udiide, nuussi sarotethaa aheedda. Unttunttu laa77uwaa shaakkiide, morkke oothi wotheedda morkketethaa godaa bare asatethan koli yeggeedda.  
\v 15 I bare huuphew ha laa77u zaretuwaappe itti ooratha asaa medhdhiide sarotethaa wothanaw, Ayihuda asatuwaa higgiyaa A azazatuwaanne wogatuwaanna ittippe dhayisseedda.  
\v 16 Kiristtoosi masqqaliyaa bolla misimaariyan dhishettiide hayqqeedda bare hayiquwan morkketethaa dhayiseedda; qassi masqqaliyaa bagganna laa77u zaretuwaakka itti asaa oothi sigethiide, Xoossaakko aheedda.  
\v 17 Kiristtoosi yiide, Xoossaappe haakkiide de7iya hinttenttoo Ayihuda gidennawanttoonne, A matan de7iya Ayihudatoo ubbaw, mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa sarotethaa odeedda. \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Isa 57:19\x* 
\v 18 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni ubbay, Ayihudatuukka Ayihuda gidennawanttukka, itti Geeshsha Ayyaanan Kiristtoosa bagganna Aawuwaa sintha shiiqanaw danddayeetto. 
\p  
\v 19 Simmi hintte Ayihuda gidenna asatuu hawaappe sinthaw allagaa woy imathaa gidikkita; ha77i hinttenne geeshshatuu itti biittaa asaa; qassi Xoossaw hintte soy asaa.  
\v 20 Yesuusi kiitteeddawanttunne timbbitiyaa odiyaawanttu baaseedda baasuwaa bolla hinttekka keexetteedita; godaa xaphuwaa minissiyaa waanna shuchchay Kiristtoosi Yesuusa.  
\v 21 I golliyaa ubbaa ittippe shiishshi oyqqiide, Xoossaa bagganna Geeshsha, Xoossaa Geeshsha golle gidana mala dichchee.  
\v 22 Hintte qassi Xoossay bare Ayyaanan de7iya golliyaa gidanaw, haratuwaa ubbaanna ittippe Kiristtoosan keexettiita. 
\c 3  
\s1 Phawuloosi Ammanenna Asaw Ootheedda Oosuwaa 
\p  
\v 1 Hewaa diraw, hinttenoo Ayihuda gidenna asatoo, taani Phawuloosi hintte diraw Kiristtoosi Yesuusa qasho asaa gideeddawe, Xoossaa woossay.  
\v 2 Xoossay bare aadho keekatethan, taani hinttena maaddanaadan, ha oosuwaa taw immeeddawaa hintte loythi siseeddita.  
\v 3 Xoossay bare xuura qofaa taw qonccissiide, taana erisseedda; taani hewaa qanthaan xaafaaddi.  
\v 4 Qassi taani xaafeeddawaa hintte nabbabiyaa wode, Kiristtoosa xuuraa taani woota akeekaadditanttonne eranaw danddayiita.  
\v 5 Beni wode asay he xuura yewuwaa sisibeenna; shin Xoossay hewaa Yesuusi kiitteedda Xoossaa naanatoonne timbbitiyaa odiyaawanttoo, Geeshsha Ayyaanan ha77i qonccisseedda.  
\v 6 Xuura yewuu hawaa; Ayihuda gidenna asay wonggalaa bagganna, Xoossaa anjjuwaa Ayihudatuwaana ittippe laattiino; unttunttu itti asatethan shaakettennaan de7iino; qassi Kiristtoosi Yesuusa bagganna Xoossay immana geeddawaa Ayihudatuwaana shaakkiino. 
\p  
\v 7 Xoossay bare oosuwaa wolqqaa bagganna taw immeedda aadho keekatethan taani ha wonggalaw qooma gidaaddi.  
\v 8 Taani geeshshatuwaa ubbaa giddon laafiyaawaa gidooppekka, Ayihuda gidenna asaw zaway bayinna Kiristtoosa duretethaa mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa odiyaa ha qaadaa Xoossay taw immeedda.  
\v 9-10 Qassi taani hewan Xoossaa xuura qofaa asaa ubbaw qonccissa odana; ubbabaa medhdheedda Xoossay bare xuura yewuwaa beni wode genthi wotheedda. Xoossay ha77i hewaa woosa golliyaa bagganna saluwaa sa7an de7iya kaappatoonne godatethay de7iyaawanttoo zaway bayinna bare aadhdheedda eratethaa qonccissanaw ootheedda.  
\v 11 Xoossay hewaa nu Godaa Kiristtoosi Yesuusa bagganna I poleedda bare medhinaa qofaadan ootheedda.  
\v 12 Nuuni Kiristtoosi Yesuusanna ittippe gidiide, A ammaniyaa ammanuwan ammanettiide, ayinne yayyennaan Xoossaa sintha shiiqanaw danddayeetto. 
\p  
\v 13 Hewaa diraw, taani hinttewaan metootiyaawan hintte hirggenna mala, hinttena woossay; ayissi gooppe, taani hintte bonchchoo metootay. 
\s1 Kiristtoosa Siiquwaa 
\p  
\v 14-15 Hewaa diraw, taani saluwaaninne sa7an de7iya ammaniyaa golliyaa asay ubbay aappe yeedda \f + \fr 3:14-15 \fq aappe yeedda: \ft Aappe denddowaan, ittuwa ittuwaa huuphiyan huuphiyan eriyaawaassa.\f* Xoossaa sinthan gulbbatay.  
\v 16-17 Xoossay bare bonchchuwaa daruwaadan, bare Geeshsha Ayyaanan, hinttenttoo hintte garssa asatethan hintte minniyaa wolqqaa immanaadaaninne, qassi ammanuwaa bagganna Kiristtoosi hintte wozanaa bare golliyaa medhdhanaadan, taani Xoossaa woossay; qassikka hintte xaphuwaa yeddiide, tokettiide siiquwan minnanaadan, Xoossaa woossay.  
\v 18 Qassi geeshshatuwaa ubbaanna Kiristtoosa siiquu ay keenaa aakentto, adussentto, dhoqqenttonne ciimmentto \f + \fr 3:18 \fq aakentto, adussentto, dhoqqenttonne ciimmentto: \ft Hawe bessiyaawe saluwan de7iyaa Yeerusalaamo woy Xoossaa siiquwaa woy Xoossaa aadho eraa woy Yesuusa masqqalew de7iyaa bilethaa.\f* eriyaa wolqqaa hinttenttu demmanaadan, taani Xoossaa woossay.  
\v 19 Eratethaappe aadhdhiyaa Kiristtoosa siiquwaa hintte eranaadaaninne qassi Xoossawaa gidiyaa ubbabaani hintte poli kumanaadan, taani Xoossaa woossay. 
\p  
\v 20-21 Simmi nu giddon oothiyaa bare wolqqaa bagganna nuuni woossiyaawaa woy qoppiyaawaa ubbaappe loythi darissi oothanaw danddayiyaa Xoossaw, woosa golliyaaninne Kiristtoosi Yesuusan ubba wode medhinaappe medhinaa gakkanaw bonchchuu gido. Amen77i. 
\c 4  
\s1 Bollaa Ittippetethaa 
\p  
\v 1 Hewaa diraw, taani Godaw oothiyaa diraw qashetteeddawe Xoossay hinttena xeeseedda xeessaw bessiyaa de7uwaa hintte de7anaadan, taani hinttena woossay.  
\v 2 Ubba wode hintte hintte huuphiyaa kawushshiyaawantta, ashikketuwaanne danddayanchchatuwaa gidite; ittuu ittuwaa maaddiyaawan hintte siiquwaa bessite.  
\v 3 Hinttena ittippe gathi qachchiyaa sarotethaan, Geeshsha Ayyaanay hinttenttoo immiya ittippetethaa naaganaw minnite.  
\v 4 Xoossay hinttena xeeseedda hidootay, hintte demmana giide naagi utteeddawe mexxi ittuwaa gidowaadan, itti asatethaynne itti Geeshsha Ayyaanay de7ee.  
\v 5 Itti Goday, itti ammanuunne itti xinqqatay de7ee.  
\v 6 Ubbaa Goday, ubbaa bagganna oothiyaawe, ubbaa giddon de7iyaawe, itti Xoossay, ubbaa Aawuu de7ee. 
\p  
\v 7 Shin Kiristtoosi immeedda imuwaadan, nuuni huuphiyan huuphiyan dumma imuwaa akkeeddo.  
\v 8 Hewaa diraw, Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q1 “I pude dhoqqasaa keseedda wode, 
\q2 omoddetteeddawantta afeedda; 
\q1 asawukka imotaa immeedda” 
\m yaage. \x - \xo 4:8 \xt Maz 68:18\x* 
\v 9 Yaatina, “Pude keseedda” giyaawe waagiyaawe? I koyiro duge wodhdheedda; hewe sa7aw hirkki wurssethasaa wodhdheedda giyaawaa.  
\v 10 Ha duge wodhdheeddawe bare huuphew A; he I ubbabaa kumanaadan, saluwaa ubbaappe dhoqqiyaasaa pude keseedda. 
\p  
\v 11 Asaw imotaa immeeddawe A; I ittuwaa ittuwaa Yesuusi kiitteeddawantta, haratuwaa timbbitiyaa odiyaawantta, qassi haratuwaa mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa odiyaawantta, qassikka haratuwaa woosa golliyaa kaalethiyaawanttanne tamaarissiyaawantta oothi suntheedda.  
\v 12 I hewaa geeshshatuu ubbay ammaniyaa asaa oosuwaa oothanaadaninne Kiristtoosa bollan keexettanaadan giigissanaw ootheedda.  
\v 13 Qassi nuuni ubbay Xoossaa Na7aa ammaninanne erina beettiyaa ittippetethaakko gakkana; nuuni Kiristtoosa polo dichchaa keenaa dicciide, donza asa gidanaadana. 
\p  
\v 14 Nuuni beetan yaanne haanne shocettiide, barenttu cimmiyaa hanotaan asaa balaa ogiyaa kaalethiyaa geniyaa asaa timirttiyaa carkkuwaa ubbaan sugettiidde, hawaappe sinthaw na7a gidanaw bessenna.  
\v 15 Shin nuuni siiqotethan tumuwaa haasayiidde, huuphe gidiyaa Kiristtoosakko ubbabaani diccanaw bessee.  
\v 16 Bollaa giddon de7iya dumma dumma shaakotay aani ittippe oyqetteeddino; qassi kumentha bollay barew imetteeddasaa ubbaan ittuu ittuwaanna gakeettiide, ittippe oyqqetti utteedda; he dumma dumma shaakotay oothanaw bessiyaawaa oothiyaa wode, kumentha bollay siiquwan dicceenne barena keexxee. 
\s1 Kiristtoosan Beettiyaa Ooratha De7uwaa 
\p  
\v 17 Hewaa diraw, taani hawaa hinttenttoo Godaa sunthan odaynne markkattay. Hintte go77i bayinna qofaa qoppiyaa Ayihuda gidenna asatuwaadan de7oppite.  
\v 18 Unttunttu wozanay dhumaani de7ee; unttunttu ayinne erennawanttanne azazettenna diraw, Xoossay immiya de7uwaappe haakkeeddino.  
\v 19 Unttunttu matan yeella giyaawe baawa; unttunttu woshummaw kajjeelanaw barenttu huuphiyaa aathi immiino; qassi tunabaa ubbaa paci bayinnaan oothanaw loythi yorattiyaawantta. 
\p  
\v 20 Shin hintte Kiristtoosawaa hewaadan tamaaribeyikkita.  
\v 21 Aabaa tumu siseeddita; qassi tumatethaykka Yesuusan de7iyaawaa, aappe tamaareeddita.  
\v 22 Hintte kase de7iya de7uwaa aggite; qassi bare cimmiyaa amuwan dhayiyaa hintte eca asatethaa dhayissite.  
\v 23 Hintte wozanaynne qofay ubbanna ooraxxanaw bessee.  
\v 24 Tumu xillotethaaninne geeshshatethan Xoossaa leemisuwan medhetteedda ooratha asatethaa mayyite. 
\p  
\v 25 Simmi worddotoppite. Nuuni ubbay Kiristtoosa asatethan itti asaa gidiyaa diraw, asay ubbay bare ishaw tumuwaa haasayanaw bessee. \x - \xo 4:25 \xt Zak 8:16\x* 
\v 26 Hanqqettite; shin hintte hanqquwan nagaraa oothoppite. Hintte hanqquwan de7ishshin, away wulloppo. \x - \xo 4:26 \xt Maz 4:4\x* 
\v 27 Xalahew xoo77iyaa immoppite.  
\v 28 Wuu77iyaa uray hawaappe sinthaw wuu77oppo; shin hewaa aggiide, hiyyeesatuwaa maaddanaw, bare kushiyan lo77obaa oothiidde daaburo. 
\p  
\v 29 Hintte haasayay sisiyaawantta go77ana mala, koshshiyaawaadan menthethiyaa lo77o qaalay hintte doonaappe kesoppe attin, iita qaalay mulekka kesoppo.  
\v 30 Xoossay hinttena woziyaa gallassaw hintte attametti utteedda Xoossaa Geeshsha Ayyaanaa kayyoyoppite.  
\v 31 Ixxiyaa hanotaa, yiilluwaa, hanqquwaa, waasuwanne cashshaa ubbaa iitatethaa ubbanna hintteppe dhayissite.  
\v 32 Ittuu ittoo keekitenne qarettite; qassi Xoossay Kiristtoosa bagganna hinttenttoo atto geeddawaadan, hinttekka ittuu ittuwaa atto giite. 
\c 5  
\s1 Poo7uwaan De7ite 
\p  
\v 1 Simmi Xoossay siiqiyaa naanatuwaadan, A malatite.  
\v 2 Qassi Kiristtoosi nuuna siiqiide, bare huuphiyaa Xoossaw nashechchiyaa yarshshuwaadaaninne imotaa udiide immeeddawaadan, hinttekka siiquwan de7anaw bessee. \x - \xo 5:2 \xt Kes 29:18; Maz 40:6\x* 
\p  
\v 3 Shin Xoossaa naanaw bessiyaawaadan, hintte giddon woshummiyaawennee tunatethaa ubbay, woy miishshaa amottiyaawe mulekka sisettoppo.  
\v 4 Yeellayiyaawenne eeya haasayay woy pathenna qidhii hinttenttoo bessennawaa gidiyaa diraw, hintte matan ubbakka de7oppo; hintte hewaa ubbaa aggiide, Xoossaa galatanaw bessee.  
\v 5 Hawaa erite; ooninne woshummiyaawaa woy tunabaa oothiyaawaa, woy miishshaa amottiyaawaa gidooppe, Kiristtoosa kawutethaanne Xoossaa kawutethaa laattanaw danddayenna; miishshaa amottiyaawe eeqaw goyinniyaawaappe dummattenna. 
\p  
\v 6 Hinttena ooninne pathenna haasayan cimmoppo; ayissi gooppe, hawaa gaasuwan Xoossaa hanqquu azazettenna asaa bolla yaana.  
\v 7 Simmi hewaa mala asaanna zuppetoppite.  
\v 8 Ayissi gooppe, kase hintte dhumaani de7eeddita; shin Godaa bagganna ha77i poo7uwan de7iita; poo7uwan de7iya asaadan poo7uwan hamettite.  
\v 9 Ayissi gooppe, poo7uu lo77otethaa, xillotethaanne tumatethaa ubbaa ayifee. 
\p  
\v 10 Godaa nashechchiyaabay ayentto tamaarite.  
\v 11 Go77i bayinna dhumaa oosuwaa qonccissi bessiteppe attin aananna walakettoppite.  
\v 12 Unttunttu geeman oothiyaawe haray atto haasayiyaawekka pokkee.  
\v 13 Shin ubbabay poo7uwaa kesiyaa wode, qoncciyaan beettana; ayissi gooppe, qoncciyaan beettiyaa ubbabay poo7uwaa.  
\v 14 Hewaa diraw, 
\q1 “Gemi77ishiyaawoo, beegotta; 
\q2 hayiquwaappekka dendda; 
\q1 Kiristtoosi new poo7issanawaa” 
\m yaagee. \f + \fr 5:14 \ft Hawe mazimuriyaa gidiidde ammaneedda asay xammaqettiyaa wode yexettiyaawaa.\f* 
\p  
\v 15 Simmi hintte waani de7intto akeekite; aadhdheedda eratethaanna de7iya asaadan de7iteppe attin, aadhdheedda eratethay bayinna asaadan de7oppite.  
\v 16 Wodii iita gidiyaa diraw, hintte wodiyaa hinttew danddayettowaadan lo77otethaw go77ettite.  
\v 17 Hewaa diraw, Goday koyyiyaawe ayentto akeekiteppe attin, eeya gidoppite. 
\p  
\v 18 Qassi hinttenan Geeshsha Ayyaanay qanxxennaan kumoppe attin, hinttena bayizziyaa woyiniyaa giyaa eessaa ushiide mathottoppite.  
\v 19 Mazimuriyaa yethaan, galatiidde yexxiyaawaaninne ayyaana yethaan ittuu ittuwaanna haasayite; qassi galatiyaa yethaaninne mazimuriyaa yexxiyaawaan hintte wozanaan Godaa galatiidde yexxite.  
\v 20 Nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa sunthan, Aawuwaa Xoossaa ubbabaw ubba wode galatite. 
\s1 Asinaabaanne Machchattibaa 
\p  
\v 21 Kiristtoosaw yayyiidde, ittuu ittoo moodettite. 
\p  
\v 22 Machchetoo, Godaw moodettiyaawaadan, hintte asinaw moodettite.  
\v 23 Ayissi gooppe, Kiristtoosi qassi woosa gollew huuphe gidiyaawaadan, asinaykka bare machchattiw huuphe; qassi Kiristtoosi bare huuphiyan, bare bollaa gidiyaa woosa golliyaa ashshiyaawaa.  
\v 24 Shin woosa golli Kiristtoosaw moodettiyaawaadan, machchetuu qassi barenttu asinaw ubbabaani moodettanaw bessee. 
\p  
\v 25 Asinatoo, Kiristtoosi woosa golliyaa siiqiide, bare huuphiyaa iziw immeeddawaadan, hinttekka hintte machchatuwaa siiqite.  
\v 26 I woosa golliyaa bare qaalaaninne haathaan meecci geeshshiide, Xoossaw dummayanaw hawaa ootheedda.  
\v 27 Kiristtoosi woosa golliyaa qitay woy deemuwaa cidhdhissiyaawe woy hewaa malatiyaawe bayinnaan, A kumentha bonchchuwaanna geeshshaanne borettennawaa udiide, bare huuphew shiishshanaw koyyeedda.  
\v 28 Simmi qassi asinay bare machchatto bare bollaadan siiqanaw bessee; bare machchatto siiqiyaawe barena siiqee.  
\v 29 Ayissi gooppe, bare bollaa ixxiyaa asay mulekka baawa; shin Kiristtoosi woosa golliyaa muziyaawaadaaninne naagiyaawaadan ooninne bare bollaa muzeenne naagee.  
\v 30 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni A bollaa dumma dumma asatethaa. 
\p  
\v 31 Xoossaa Maxaafay; “Hewaa diraw, attumawe bare aawuwaanne bare daayo aggiide, bare machchattina ittippe de7ana; unttunttu laa77uukka itti ashuwaa gidana” yaagee. \x - \xo 5:31 \xt Dom 2:24\x* 
\v 32 Ha xuuray wolqqaama tumatethaa; shin taani hawe Kiristtoosabaanne woosa golliyaabaa odee yaagay.  
\v 33 Gidooppekka, qassi asinay huuphiyan huuphiyan machchiyaa bare huuphiyaadan siiqanaw bessee; machchattakka bare asinaa bonchchanaw bessee. 
\c 6  
\s1 Yeleeddawanttubaanne Yeletteedda Naanatuwaabaa 
\p  
\v 1 Naatoo, hinttena yeleeddawanttoo Godaa bonchchiyaawaadan azazettite; ayissi gooppe, hawe oothanaw bessiyaawaa. \x - \xo 6:1 \xt Qol 3:20\x* 
\v 2-3 “New ubbabay lo77anaadaaninne sa7an ne laythay aduqqanaadan, ne aawuwaanne ne daayo bonchcha” giya azazuu Xoossay immana geedda hidootaana de7iya koyiro azazuwaa. \x - \xo 6:2-3 \xt Kes 20:12; Zar 5:16\x* 
\p  
\v 4 Aawatoo, hintte hintte naanatuwaa Godaa seeraaninne zoriyaan dichchiteppe attin, unttuntta hanqqethoppite. \x - \xo 6:4 \xt Qol 3:21\x* 
\s1 Godatuwaabaanne Ayllatuwaabaa 
\p  
\v 5 Ayillatoo, Kiristtoosaw oothiyaawaadan, hintte godatoo yashshatethaaninne kokkorssaan suure wozanaappe azazettite. \x - \xo 6:5 \xt Qol 3:22-25\x* 
\v 6 Xoossay geeddawaa oothiyaawanttudan, Kiristtoosa ayillatuwaadan, wozanaappe oothiteppe attin, asaa nashechchanaw oothiyaawaadan, asay be7o giide oothoppite.  
\v 7 Asaw gidennaan Godaw oothiyaawaadan, dhibennaan wozanaappe oothite.  
\v 8 Ayille gidina woy womaanuwaa gidina, I oothiyaa lo77o ooso ubbaw Goday huuphiyan huuphiyan woyitanawaa eriita. 
\p  
\v 9 Godatoo, hintte ayilletuwaa naassiyaawaa aggiide, unttunttoo hewaadan oothite; hinttenanne unttuntta gathi mooddiyaa Goday, oonanne maaddi pirddennawe, saluwan de7iyaawaa eriita. 
\s1 Xoossaa Olaa Miishshatuwaabaa 
\p  
\v 10 Wurssethaan, Godaaninne A wolqqaama wolqqan ubba wode minnite.  
\v 11 Xalahiyaa iita cimuwaa te77anaw hintte danddayana mala, Xoossay hinttenttoo immiya ollaa mayuwaa ubbaa mayyite.  
\v 12 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni bolla saluwaa de7iya iita ayyaana wolqqatuwaanna, mooddiyaawanttunna, godatethay de7iyaawanttunnanne ha dhuma biittaa mooddiyaawanttunna olettiyaawaappe attin, asaanna olettokko. 
\p  
\v 13 Hewaa diraw, iita gallassaan \f + \fr 6:13 \fq iita gallassaan: \ft Ha77i de7iyaa wodiyaa woy hayquwaa gallassaa woy wurssethaa pirdda woy mura gallassaa giyaawaa.\f* te77anawunne qassi wurssethay gakkanaw wadhettowaappe guyyiyan, minni eqqanaw hintte danddayana mala, Xoossaa olaa miishshaa ubbaa oyqqite.  
\v 14-15 Hewaa diraw, xeessan saqqiyaa dancciyaawaadan tumatethaa dancciide, tiraan wothiyaa olaa miishshaadan xillotethaa mayyiide, hintte gediyaan caammaa wothiyaawaadan sarotethaa mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa odanaw giigiide, minni eqqite. \x - \xo 6:14-15 \xt Isa 52:7\x* 
\v 16 He ubbaappe aathiide, xalahii yeddiyaa wonddaafiyaa tamaa ubbaa toyissanaw, ammanuwaa ubba wode gonddalliyaadan oyqqite.  
\v 17 Atotethaa huuphiyan wothiyaa birataa qoobiyaadan wothite; qassi Geeshsha Ayyaanaa mashshaa gideedda Xoossaa qaalaa oyqqite. \x - \xo 6:17 \xt Isa 59:17\x* 
\v 18 Xoossaa woossiiddinne A maaduwaa oochchiidde, ubba wode Geeshsha Ayyaanan Xoossaa woossite. Hewaa diraw, minnite; salettoppite; geeshshatuwaa ubbaw Xoossaa ubba wode woossite. 
\p  
\v 19 Qassi taani yayyennaan wonggalaa xuuraa odanaw, Xoossay ta doonaa dooyyiide, haasayiyaawaa immanaadan, tawukka Xoossaa woossite.  
\v 20 Taani ha77i qashuwan de7ooppekka, ha wonggalaa diraw taani kiitetteeddawaa; taani aabaa taw bessiyaawaadan yayyennaan odana mala, taw Xoossaa woossite. 
\s1 Wurssetha Sarotaa 
\p  
\v 21 Shin taani waana de7inttonne ayaa oothaytantto hinttekka eranaadan, nu siiqo ishay, Godaa oosuwan ammanetteedda qoomay Tikiqoosi, tawaa ubbaa hinttenttoo odanawaa. \x - \xo 6:21 \xt Kit 20:4; 2Xi 4:12\x*\x - \xo 6:21 \xt Qol 4:7-8\x* 
\v 22 Nuuni ubbay waani de7intto hinttenttoo odiide, hinttena minissana mala, taani A hinttekko kiittaaddi. 
\p  
\v 23 Xoossaa Aawuwaappenne Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosappe sarotethaynne siiqotethay ammanuwaana ittippe ishatuwaa ubbaw gido;  
\v 24 Dochchenna siiquwan nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa siiqiyaa ubbatuwaanna Xoossaa aadho keekatethay gido. Amen77i.